 transition-colors">社群媒體管理 (Social Media Management)</h4><p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">製作高質內容，提升品牌價值與顧客參與度。</p></div></div></div></a><a class="group" href="/design/"><div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 hover:border-yellow-400 h-full"><div class="flex items-start space-x-4"><div class="flex-shrink-0"><div class="w-12 h-12 bg-yellow-400 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-yellow-500 transition-colors"><i class="fas fa-palette text-white text-xl"></i></div></div><div class="flex-1"><h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2 group-hover:text-yellow-600 transition-colors">平面及包裝設計 (Design)</h4><p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">專業設計宣傳海報、單張及產品包裝，提升品牌視覺吸引力。</p></div></div></div></a><a class="group" href="/digital-ads/"><div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 hover:border-yellow-400 h-full"><div class="flex items-start space-x-4"><div class="flex-shrink-0"><div class="w-12 h-12 bg-yellow-400 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-yellow-500 transition-colors"><i class="fab fa-google text-white text-xl"></i></div></div><div class="flex-1"><h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2 group-hover:text-yellow-600 transition-colors">數位廣告投放 (Digital Advertising)</h4><p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Google Ads / Facebook &amp; Instagram 廣告投放。</p></div></div></div></a></div><div class="text-center mt-16"><a class="inline-flex items-center bg-yellow-400 hover:bg-yellow-500 text-gray-800 px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold text-lg transition-colors" href="/contact/"><i class="fas fa-trophy mr-2"></i>成為行業第一</a></div></div></section><section class="py-20 bg-gray-50"><div class="container mx-auto px-4"><div class="text-center mb-16"><h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">成功案例</h2><p class="text-gray-600 text-lg mb-4">我們為各行各業客戶提供的成功解決方案</p><