ttom:0;color:transparent" src="https://cdn.sanity.io/images/q1lbcmln/production/bc677b10e9a203ecd8763a5959f5061574131302-469x398.png"/><div class="absolute top-4 left-4 bg-yellow-400 text-gray-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold">精選案例</div></div><div class="p-6"><div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-2"><span class="text-sm text-blue-600 font-medium">Other</span><span class="text-sm text-gray-500">2025</span></div><h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2 line-clamp-2"> 2023 ViuTV drama 殺手廢J - Title-Sponsorship SOW:</h3><p class="text-gray-600 mb-4 line-clamp-2"><span class="font-semibold">客戶：</span>ViuTV</p><div class="mb-4"><div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1"><span class="bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded-full">SEO</span></div></div><a class="inline-flex items-center text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 font-medium text-sm" href="/case/2023-viutv-drama-j-title-sponsorship-sow/">查看詳細案例<svg class="w-4 h-4 ml-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"></path></svg></a></div></div><div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300"><div class="relative h-48 overflow-hidden"><img alt=" HSBC One - 2021 投資A0變世一 Social video (EP1-3) " loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" class="object-cover hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent" src="https://cdn.sanity.io/images/q1lbcmln/production/1c122306b9c48c0d9dcecaf1f2e212176049fa45-439x375.png"/><div class="absolute top-4 left-4 bg-yellow-400 text-gray-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold">精選案例</div></div><div class="p-6"><div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-2"><span class="text-sm text-blue-600 font-medium">Other</span><span class="text-sm text-gray-500">2025</span></div><h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2 line-clamp-2"> HSBC One - 2021 投資A0變世一 Social video (EP1-3) </h3><p class="text-gray-600 mb-4 line-clamp-2"><span class="font-semibold">客戶：</span> HSBC</p><div class="mb-4"><div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1"><span class="bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded-full">SEO</span></div></div><a class="inline-flex items-center text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 font-medium text-sm" href="/case/hsbc-one-2021-a0-social-video-ep1-3/">查看詳細案例<svg class="w-4 h-4 ml-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"></path></svg></a></div></div></div><div class="text-center mt-12"><a class="inline-flex items-center bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold transition-colors" href="/cases/">查看所有案例<svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"></path></svg></a></div></div></section><section class="py-20 bg-gray-50"><div class="container mx-auto px-4"><div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center"><div><h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-8">最適合您的市場推廣公司</h2><div class="text-gray-600 text-lg leading-relaxed space-y-6"><p>Big Bang Marketing 是一間新創的全方位行銷公司，雲集來自不同 領域的行銷專家，致力為客戶提供量身訂製的行銷解決方案。 我們的服務涵蓋多個行業，包括美容、眼鏡、僱傭中介、教育、零售 等，無論線上還是線下，我們都能協助企業拓展市場，提升品牌曝 光，增加業績，並與世界接軌。</p></div><div class="mt-8 space-y-4"><div class="flex items-center text-gray-700"><span class="text-yellow-500 text-xl mr-3">✯</span><span>最全面的成長營銷策略</span></div><div class="flex items-center text-gray-700"><span class="text-yellow-500 text-xl mr-3">✯</span><span>嵌入式營銷團隊，最理解您企業業務的營銷公司</span></div><div class="flex items-center text-gray-700"><span class="text-yellow-500 text-xl mr-3">✯</span><span>由多名具豐富營銷經驗的 Marketing專家主理</span></div><div class="flex items-center text-gray-700"><span class="text-yellow-500 text-xl mr-3">✯</span><span>最全面、最有效、性價比最高的營銷方案</span></div></div><a class="inline-flex items-center bg-yellow-400 hover:bg-yellow-500 text-gray-800 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold mt-8 transition-colors" href="/contact/"><i class="fas fa-trophy mr-2"></i>成為行業第一</a></div><div class="relative"><img alt="營銷數據及工作環境" loading="lazy" width="800" height="699" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="rounded-lg shadow-xl w-full h-auto" style="color:transparent" src="/營銷數據及工作環境.jpg.webp"/></div></div></div></section><section class="py-20 bg-gray-50"><div class="container mx-auto px-4"><div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center"><div><h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-8">什麼是成長營銷 Growth Marketing?</h2><div class="text-gray-600 text-lg leading-relaxed space-y-6"><p>在 Big Bang Marketing，我們相信行銷不只是曝光與點擊，更 是一場關於「增長」的實驗。</p><p>Growth Marketing 成長營銷 有別於傳統行銷模式 —— 我們 不單追求短期的廣告成效，而是以 企業的整體增長 為核心，從 潛在客戶開發到轉換與留存，構建出可持續的增長引擎。</p></div><a class="inline-flex items-center bg-yellow-400 hover:bg-yellow-500 text-gray-800 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold mt-8 transition-colors" href="/contact/"><i class="fas fa-trophy mr-2"></i>成為行業第一</a></div><div class="relative"><div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-600 to-purple-600 rounded-lg p-8 text-white"><h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">🎯 我們怎樣推動增長？</h3><div class="space-y-4 text-gray-100 leading-relaxed"><p>每個品牌都擁有獨特的DNA，Big Bang 會根據企業階段與市場環境，制定專屬的成長策略，並 透過實驗與數據驗證持續優化：</p><ul class="space-y-3"><li class="flex items-start space-x-3"><span class="text-yellow-400 font-bold">●</span><span>SEO &amp; 內容行銷：提升品牌搜尋能見度，讓你的內容在正確的時間出現在正確的人面前。</span></li><li class="flex items-start space-x-3"><span class="text-yellow-400 font-bold">●</span><span>社交媒體行銷：結合創意與分析，放大品牌聲量，吸引高互動的潛在客戶。</span></li><li class="flex items-start space-x-3"><span class="text-yellow-400 font-bold">●</span><span>轉換率優化（CRO）：以數據為導向，持續測試與改良，將流量轉化為真實收益。</span></li><li class="flex items-start space-x-3"><span class="text-yellow-400 font-bold">●</span><span>行銷自動化與AI應用：以智慧工具自動化流程，讓行銷更快、更準、更有效</span></li></ul></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class="py-20 bg-gray-50"><div class="container mx-auto px-4"><div class="text-center mb-16"><h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">FAQ // 成長營銷常見問題</h2><div class="w-24 h-1 bg-yellow-400 mx-auto mb-8"></div><p class="text-gray-600 text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto">解答您對成長營銷最常見的疑問，讓您更了解如何運用數據驅動的營銷策略實現業務增長。</p></div><div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto"><div class="space-y-6"><div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6"><h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3 flex items-center"><span class="bg-yellow-400 text-gray-800 rounded-full w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold mr-3">1</span>什麼是成長營銷 (Growth Marketing)？</h3><div class="pl-11"><p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">成長營銷是一種以數據驅動的營銷方法，專注於企業的持續增長。與傳統營銷不同，成長營銷強調通過測試、優化和迭代來實現可持續的業務擴張。</p></div></div><div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6"><h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3 flex items-center"><span class="bg-yellow-400 text-gray-800 rounded-full w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold mr-3">2</span>成長營銷與傳統營銷有什麼區別？</h3><div class="pl-11"><p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">傳統營銷通常關注品牌知名度和一次性銷售，而成長營銷更注重長期價值、客戶留存和可持續增長。它使用數據分析來優化每個營銷渠道，並不斷測試新策略。</p></div></div><div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6"><h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3 flex items-center"><span class="bg-yellow-400 text-gray-800 rounded-full w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold mr-3">3</span>Big Bang Marketing 如何幫助企業成長？</h3><div class="pl-11"><p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">我們提供全方位的成長營銷服務，包括市場策劃、SEO優化、社交媒體營銷、內容營銷等。我們會根據您的業務特點制定個性化的成長策略，並持續監控和優化效果。</p></div></div><div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6"><h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3 flex items-center"><span class="bg-yellow-400 text-gray-800 rounded-full w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold mr-3">4</span>成長營銷需要多長時間才能看到效果？</h3><div class="pl-11"><p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">成長營銷的效果因行業和策略而異。一般來說，SEO優化可能需要3-6個月才能看到顯著效果，而社交媒體營銷和內容營銷可能會更快見效。我們會定期向您報告進展。</p></div></div><div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6"><h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3 flex items-center"><span class="bg-yellow-400 text-gray-800 rounded-full w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold mr-3">5</span>我的企業適合成長營銷嗎？</h3><div class="pl-11"><p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">幾乎所有企業都可以從成長營銷中受益，特別是那些希望實現可持續增長的企業。無論您是初創公司還是成熟企業，我們都能根據您的具體情況制定合適的策略。</p></div></div><div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6"><h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3 flex items-center"><span class="bg-yellow-400 text-gray-800 rounded-full w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold mr-3">6</span>成長營銷的投資回報率如何？</h3><div class="pl-11"><p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">根據我們的經驗，成長營銷的平均投資回報率可以達到3-7倍。通過精確的目標定位和持續優化，我們能夠最大化您的營銷投資效益。</p></div></div><div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6"><h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3 flex items-center"><span class="bg-yellow-400 text-gray-800 rounded-full w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold mr-3">7</span>如何開始實施成長營銷策略？</h3><div class="pl-11"><p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">首先需要進行市場分析和目標設定，然後制定詳細的營銷計劃。我們建議從一個核心渠道開始，逐步擴展到多渠道整合營銷。</p></div></div></div></div><div class="text-center mt-16"><div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto"><h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">還有其他問題嗎？</h3><p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">我們的成長營銷專家隨時準備解答您的疑問，幫您制定最適合的營銷策略。</p><a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center bg-yellow-400 hover:bg-yellow-500 text-gray-800 px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold transition-colors"><i class="fas fa-envelope mr-2"></i>聯絡我們</a></div></div></div></section><section class="py-20 bg-white"><div class="container mx-auto px-4"><div class="text-center mb-16"><h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">服務合作伙伴</h2><div class="flex justify